{
  "id": "69b929122a43d542649d87a2",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:批判には対案を",
  "created": 1773742378,
  "updated": 1773742399,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b929122a43d542649d87a2",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:批判には対案を",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742378,
      "updated": 1773742378
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292a0000000000d7474f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742378,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74750",
      "text": "「はいはーい！今日のテーマは『[批判には対案を]』ね！いやこれマジで大事じゃね？ネットでも“それダメ！”だけ言って消える人、わりといるじゃんw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74751",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74752",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74753",
      "text": "「ええ……否定の言葉だけが宙に残ると、まるで行き場を失った小舟のようでございますね。受け取った側も、どこへ向かえばよいのか分からなくなってしまいますもの」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74754",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74755",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74756",
      "text": "「的確な比喩だね。結論から言えば、“批判＋代替案”は意思決定の基本プロセス。問題提起だけでは、改善ループが回らない」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74757",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74758",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74759",
      "text": "「出た、りかの難しいやつw つまり、“ダメ出しするなら、次どうすればいいかも言おうぜ”ってことでしょ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7475a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7475b",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7475c",
      "text": "「その理解で正しい。ソフトウェア開発でも同じ。バグ報告だけでなく、再現手順や修正案があると解決速度が上がる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7475d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7475e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7475f",
      "text": "「たしかに……ただ、誰しもすぐに“よい案”を思いつけるわけではありませんわよね。心に浮かぶのは、まず違和感や戸惑いでございますから」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74760",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74761",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74762",
      "text": "「それな〜。“なんか違う！”って気持ち先に来るやつ。で、言いたくなっちゃうw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74763",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74764",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74765",
      "text": "「そこは段階を分ければいい。一次反応としての違和感はOK。ただし、公に発信するなら“暫定案”でも添える。未完成でも価値はある」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74766",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74767",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74768",
      "text": "「“仮でもいいから出せ”ってことか。β版ってやつねw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74769",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7476a",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7476b",
      "text": "「未熟な案であっても、灯りのように道を照らすことはできますものね。（微笑）誰かがその灯りを受けて、よりよい形へと育ててくださるかもしれません」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7476c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7476d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7476e",
      "text": "「協働的改善、いわゆるコラボレーション。オープンソース文化に近い。例えばGitHubでも“Issue”には改善案や代替設計を書くのが推奨されている",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7476f",
      "text": "https://docs.github.com/en/issues 」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74770",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74771",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74772",
      "text": "「おお、ちゃんとルールあるんだ。てかそれ、学校のグループワークにも必要じゃね？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74773",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74774",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74775",
      "text": "「ええ……“それは違うと思います”とだけ告げるより、“このようにしてみてはいかがでしょう”と添えるほうが、場の空気もやわらぎますわね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74776",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74777",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74778",
      "text": "「心理的安全性の観点でも重要。否定のみは防御反応を引き起こすが、代案があれば建設的議論に移行しやすい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74779",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7477a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7477b",
      "text": "「つまり、“ケンカになりにくい批判”ってことか。神じゃんそれ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7477c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7477d",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7477e",
      "text": "「ただ……あまりに論理ばかりを重ねますと、言葉が冷たく響いてしまうこともございます。心を添えることも、忘れたくありませんわ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7477f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74780",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74781",
      "text": "「同意。ロジックとエンパシー（共感）のバランスが必要」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74782",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74783",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74784",
      "text": "「おっ、意見そろったじゃん。じゃあまとめいくよ〜！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74785",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74786",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74787",
      "text": "「要点を整理する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74788",
      "text": " 1. 批判だけでは改善は進まない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74789",
      "text": " 2. 未完成でもよいので代替案を提示する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7478a",
      "text": " 3. 共感を添えると対立を避けられる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7478b",
      "text": "」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7478c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7478d",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7478e",
      "text": "「ええ……批判とは、壊すための言葉ではなく、よりよくするための祈りのようなもの。そう考えられたら、きっと優しい世界になりますわね（静かに微笑む）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d7478f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74790",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292b0000000000d74791",
      "text": "「うわ〜、締めが文学すぎるw でもいい感じ！じゃ今日はここまで！みんなも“ダメ出し＋アイデア”でいこーぜ！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742379,
      "updated": 1773742379
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292d0000000000d74792",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742382,
      "updated": 1773742382
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9292e0000000000d74793",
      "text": "#2026-03-17",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773742382,
      "updated": 1773742399
    },
